Class MockHttpTransport

Mock for HttpTransport.

Implementation is thread-safe, as long as .supportedOptionalMethods is not modified directly (which is deprecated usage). For maximum efficiency, applications should use a single globally-shared instance of the HTTP transport.

@author Yaniv Inbar @since 1.3
